17
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:57,479
Want me to teach him a lesson for you?

18
00:00:57,759 --> 00:00:59,000
No need to bicker with that kind of person

19
00:01:00,479 --> 00:01:04,159
Isn't this Great Technician Zheng?

20
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,280
