103
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:45,960
Yingrong!

104
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,039
Yingrong!

105
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,240
Don't scare Mom.

106
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,919
Is she okay?

107
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:55,439
Don't scare Mom!

108
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,719
Yingrong!

109
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,639
Don't scare Mom.

110
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,479
