126
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,959
Yingrong, are you okay?

127
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,199
Mom

128
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,079
Yingrong

129
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,279
Mom

130
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,759
Are you okay?

131
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:59,160
