135
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,879
It's only right to act bravely

136
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,560
Xiaochuan

137
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,079
Mom

138
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:10,800
Xiaochuan

139
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,160
Mom, I saved someone

140
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,199
That Wang Yingrong...

141
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:13,839
And her...

142
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:15,279
I pulled them both out

143
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,360
Thank you all

144
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,319
You're welcome

145
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,560
If you really want to thank us,

146
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,879
