Exactly

163
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,800
Our Xiaochuan is a good swimmer

164
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,879
One good deed a day

165
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:51,879
It's only right, it's only right

166
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:53,759
Better to live poorly than to die

167
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,480
