168
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,639
Do you hear me?

169
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,600
Let's go, let's go back

170
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,560
I'm telling you, this bad temper of yours...

171
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,720
