172
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,040
You can't get over even the smallest thing

173
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,040
Throwing yourself in the river to commit suicide

174
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,000
Aren't you afraid people will laugh their heads off?

175
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:21,360
Mom

176
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:24,160
I really didn't want to die

177
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,000
I went to save someone

178
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,600
It was Zheng Xiaochuan who saved the person

179
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,639
You threw yourself in the river to commit suicide

180
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:32,519
You were saved by someone else

181
