189
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,480
Whenever I'm unhappy, I just dive into the river

190
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,160
What is going on?

191
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,879
You ask me, who am I supposed to ask?

192
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,000
How did I give birth to...

193
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,759
