196
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,279
You...

197
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:01,680
Fine, fine, fine

198
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,000
Get out

199
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,800
Go talk outside

200
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:03,839
We won't talk, we won't talk anymore

201
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:05,160
Hurry up and drink the ginger soup before you sleep

202
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,720
She's fine

203
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,600
Why are you back?

204
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,399
Did you ask for leave?

205
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,639
Nothing is more important than our daughter

206
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:29,680
I warmed it up for you

207
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,759
You are suspended now

208
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,920
What are your thoughts for the future?

209
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:46,560
Before, it was all state-owned economy,

210
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,279
