211
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:51,600
Now the radio encourages the self-employed to do business

212
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:54,079
I read the Chongjiang Daily very carefully

213
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:55,959
There are still self-employed people now

214
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,319
I've planned out my future

215
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,600
I'll start a small business myself

216
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,839
You've thought it through?

217
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,800
Did Mom send you to talk to me?

218
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,360
Mom told me to endure it

219
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,680
But for things I didn't do

220
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,040
I just won't admit to them

221
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,319
I'm not willing to endure it

222
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:15,360
No matter how much I suffer later

223
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,319
I'll accept it

224
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,079
I won't go back to the factory

225
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,160
Alright

226
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,800
Ever since you were little

227
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,959
you've had a mind of your own

228
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,519
On one hand

229
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,959
caring for your older sister

230
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,240
and on the other

231
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,839
taking care of your younger sister

232
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,160
Later on

233
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,519
if you can't keep going on your own

234
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:35,919
and don't want to get married

235
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,360
I, your dad

236
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,519
can still support you

237
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:50,000
Mom would beat me to death then

238
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,759
Besides

239
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:54,679
I need to eat fried eggs every day

240
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:55,960
Can you afford to support me?

241
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,279
Dad

242
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,240
you don't need to worry about me

243
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,960
I've already figured out what to do

244
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,720
I will do well

245
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,519
our whole family will do well

246
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,399
and no one will be able to bully us

247
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,440
What are you doing in broad daylight?

248
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,480
It smells so bad

249
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:45,919
Hey!

250
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,919
