253
00:09:56,279 --> 00:09:56,799
Hey!

254
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,679
Zheng Minjiang

255
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,120
Zheng Xiaochuan

256
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,279
Auntie

257
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,320
Auntie

258
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:16,279
Auntie

259
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:18,759
Auntie

260
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,200
Someone come quick!

261
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:25,639
Someone come quick!

262
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,559
Someone come quick!

263
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:29,200
