272
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,919
It is indeed carbon monoxide poisoning.

273
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,399
Luckily she was brought in time.

274
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:53,679
Come sign here.

275
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,440
I'm not her family.

276
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,279
