283
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,960
It's all my fault back then.

284
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,200
I didn't see clearly.

285
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:19,159
If I knew whose daughter she was,

286
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,360
I'd go over to propose.

287
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:22,120
Bring her home as a daughter-in-law.

288
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:22,919
Yes.

289
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:25,600
But that Minjiang of yours,

290
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,639
