291
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,679
If not for Director Zhang's harassment,

292
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:32,799
Yingrong wouldn't have jumped in the river out of anger.

293
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,600
And they say,

294
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,080
your Minjiang

295
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,799
even kissed her.

296
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:38,440
Everyone saw it.

297
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,480
No such thing.

298
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,399
Impossible.

299
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,480
Our Minjiang was saving a life.

300
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,960
That's not called kissing.

301
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,559
Don't talk nonsense here.

302
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,399
Xuelin.

303
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:52,639
But your Number Three is capable.

304
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:54,159
He's quite promising.

305
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:57,440
He actually saved Old Fang's daughter.

306
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,000
Our Number Three,

307
00:11:59,000 --> 00:11:59,960
with that personality of his,

308
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,440
is naturally the heroic type.

309
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,600
Even if it wasn't a nouveau riche this time,

310
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,519
he would have saved her anyway.

311
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:09,879
Xiaochuan,

312
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,159
come out.

313
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:13,159
Tell the Aunties,

314
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:15,200
how you saved her.

315
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,480
Mom!

316
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,519
Why broadcast such a small thing?

317
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:21,240
No man would just stand by and watch.

318
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,799
Why tell everyone?

319
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,879
Look at our Number Three.

320
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,559
Isn't this the nouveau riche Fang family?

321
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:32,919
By the looks of it,

322
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:34,759
they must be here to thank you.

323
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:36,000
Here to thank us.

324
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:41,720
Rich people are just different.

325
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,960
You shouldn't have brought anything.

326
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,440
And so much good wine too.

327
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,080
Are you Yingrong's mother?
